1.	download the extension by executing 'git clone https://github.com/FriendOfTux/YubIcon'

2.	move extension folder to '~/.local/share/gnome-shell/extensions/YubIcon@FriendOfTux'

3.	compile schema by executing 'glib-compile-schemas schemas' in the extensions folder

4.1	restart the gnome shell / reboot the system
4.2	start the extension from the gnome-extension manager
